---
// Experience
---

<section id="experience" class="py-24">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">

    <div class="fade-in mb-14">
      <span class="section-marker">// 01</span>
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#d8eaf5]">Experience</h2>
      <div class="w-8 h-[1.5px] mt-2" style="background: linear-gradient(to right, #00e5b4, transparent);"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="relative pl-8 space-y-14" style="border-left: 1px solid #162d48;">

      <!-- Entry 1 — current -->
      <div class="fade-in relative">
        <div class="absolute -left-[2.35rem] top-1 w-2.5 h-2.5 rounded-full bg-[#00e5b4]"
             style="box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px #060e1c, 0 0 0 5px rgba(0,229,180,0.3);"></div>

        <span class="inline-block text-xs font-mono text-[#00e5b4] mb-2 opacity-70 tracking-wider">
          Apr 2024 – Present
        </span>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-[#d8eaf5] leading-snug">
          Senior Data Analyst
          <span class="text-[#5a7a96] font-normal"> — an Indonesian insurtech, Jakarta</span>
        </h3>

        <ul class="mt-4 space-y-2 text-sm text-[#8fb0cc]">
          {[
            'Built a dbt data warehouse replacing 4–6 hr/day manual Excel workflows, reducing reporting time to under 10 minutes',
            'Designed Tableau dashboards presented directly to the Board of Directors for weekly insurance portfolio reviews',
            'Developed dbt models across health, motor, marine, and reinsurance lines of business',
            'Automated data pipelines for claim, premium, and policy reporting across multiple insurance products',
          ].map((item) => (
            <li class="flex gap-2.5">
              <span class="text-[#00e5b4] mt-0.5 shrink-0 font-mono">›</span>
              {item}
            </li>
          ))}
        </ul>

        <div class="mt-5 flex flex-wrap gap-2">
          {['dbt', 'Databricks', 'AWS Redshift', 'Python', 'SQL', 'Tableau', 'Metabase'].map((t) => (
            <span class="skill-pill">{t}</span>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Entry 2 -->
      <div class="fade-in relative">
        <div class="absolute -left-[2.35rem] top-1 w-2.5 h-2.5 rounded-full bg-[#0c1a2d]"
             style="border: 1.5px solid #4d94ff; box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px #060e1c;"></div>

        <span class="inline-block text-xs font-mono text-[#5a7a96] mb-2 tracking-wider">
          Feb 2023 – Feb 2024
        </span>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-[#d8eaf5] leading-snug">
          Business Intelligence Analyst
          <span class="text-[#5a7a96] font-normal"> — a major Indonesian mining company, Jakarta</span>
        </h3>

        <ul class="mt-4 space-y-2 text-sm text-[#8fb0cc]">
          {[
            'Led full Teradata-to-Snowflake migration, including ETL pipeline build and data validation',
            'Built a SAP BusinessObjects data mart for the UOMS division, consolidating operational data sources',
            'Delivered Power BI dashboards for the dewatering operations team, improving real-time visibility',
            'Worked in an Agile / daily-scrum environment within a cross-functional data team',
          ].map((item) => (
            <li class="flex gap-2.5">
              <span class="text-[#4d94ff] mt-0.5 shrink-0 font-mono">›</span>
              {item}
            </li>
          ))}
        </ul>

        <div class="mt-5 flex flex-wrap gap-2">
          {['Teradata', 'Snowflake', 'SAP BusinessObjects', 'Power BI', 'SAP Data Services'].map((t) => (
            <span class="skill-pill">{t}</span>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>
